 in purchasing behaviour of consumers and education campaigns were effective in reducing the trade of bats and primates, animal groups likely to be implicated in the trans\u00ad mission of Ebola.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Funk, Stephan M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fa, Julia E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ajong, Stephanie N.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Eniang, Edem A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Dendi, Daniele", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Di Vittorio, Massimiliano", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Petrozzi, Fabio", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Amadi, NioKing", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Akani, Godfrey C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Luiselli, Luca", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/3359f39b868f5a4c968dd2178513a447", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/aa7373157bbf83107a83ad25b0ce5c4f613b958e1a6e70f1e71ba00d5172542d", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/6F5XMD9T", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/6F5XMD9T", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/b4c46b2b96b637038cca86946aeaf03f!/b41311-43974", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"pages": "109024", "title": "Biological Conservation", "volu